{"tid":1534742,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"913-915 揸三日春袋！！！","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T15:56:10.000Z","uid":95138,"like":118,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"39687f512bd2e379cf8125dafa34aa50d054c6d1","tid":1534742,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:02:43.000Z","msg":"如果到時政府仲係唔回應五大訴求<br />\n我地就一揸揸夠三日春袋<br />\n橫掂有三日假<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三日假 揸爆佢春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主正on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084fa42e94e74107be26108df4be3058f43339f4","tid":1534742,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:02:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e1b0fb1675398d16c1fb07ed3f636da1be14add","tid":1534742,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:03:27.000Z","msg":"我跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d902a4bdf0644a40b2d469e83660586ccb18c3d2","tid":1534742,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:03:52.000Z","msg":"講個笑話：禁制令<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28f885028931ca9de3918bac152880dd0fdf06b","tid":1534742,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a5f3e4cc3215505d17376b8d9938fff140a462","tid":1534742,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:05:01.000Z","msg":"913 914 915 1pm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c754697d44afec7db90a25e9d0fe480814faa02","tid":1534742,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:06:00.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"a44ff5f0372d8cc30cb5c5c0c09133e282903d1e","tid":1534742,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:08:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ce7241eb536cec43ceda228d729ce33150a4285","tid":1534742,"uid":252960,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"老老實實，三日連續不切實際"},{"pid":"fc595c3b515bd4fa20bea720d3210ab91509a7da","tid":1534742,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ce7241eb536cec43ceda228d729ce33150a4285","tid":1534742,"uid":252960,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"老老實實，三日連續不切實際"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"算係升級<br />\n之前塞一日 第二日就清番D機"},{"pid":"87c4d333f2c07cdd801120bebcee69ba1e698079","tid":1534742,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:19:39.000Z","msg":"揸緊春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31e26eda96b53d625cd406a7f8e58bc1f164fda","tid":1534742,"uid":241904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:20:11.000Z","msg":"一定要繼續入機場<br />\n以街坊裝入<br />\n去睇飛機升降<br />\n口號都唔洗叫<br />\n如果停鐵停車就慢慢等<br />\n咁多遊客D狗做唔到D咩<br />\n佢一亂拉人就全世界睇住"},{"pid":"6db33b74baee12d35af8bf9fc40b2f6a2d1dd45e","tid":1534742,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:20:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3732f1700ba73227a6ce21e742440891f1d87fb","tid":1534742,"uid":291372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"39687f512bd2e379cf8125dafa34aa50d054c6d1","tid":1534742,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:02:43.000Z","msg":"如